# wexample-filestate-python

Helpers for Python.

Version: 0.0.41

## Requirements

- Python >=3.10

## Dependencies

- pydantic>=2,<3
- wexample-filestate==0.0.51

## Installation

```bash
pip install wexample-filestate-python
```
